<h2>Norwood Road</h2>


<p>From 22:00 Monday 27 May until late October 2019, Route 315 will not serve Canterbury Grove, Royal Circus, York Hill, Norwood Road, Norwood High Street and Ernest Avenue.</p>

<p>A diversion will be in place via Leigham Court Road, Crown Lane (Crown Point) and Knights Hill, with buses terminating at Norwood Bus Garage. The diversion will affect buses travelling towards West Norwood only. Buses towards Balham will run as normal.</p>
