<h2>Feltham station bridge works</h2>

<p>From 29 May 2018 to late&nbsp;August 2019, Hounslow Road will be temporarily closed between New Road and Hanworth Road to all traffic and pedestrians in both directions. This is while improvement works are carried out to the railway bridge at Feltham train station.</p>

<p>For the duration of the works the following bus routes will be diverted:</p>

<p>90, 117, 235, 285, 490, 635, H25 and H26.</p>

<p>The area may be busier than usual. Please check before you travel and allow extra time for your journey.</p>
