<h2>Liverpool Street bus station&nbsp;works</h2>

<p><strong>Bus routes 11, 133, 153, N11, N133 affected</strong></p>

<p>From 23:30 on Monday 6 November 2017 until September 2019, Liverpool Street bus Station is closed to allow construction work on the adjacent Broadgate site&nbsp;redevelopment.</p>

<p>Routes 11, 133, N11 and N133:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Finish at Old Broad Street, near Great Winchester Street (stop Z), approximately 275m from Liverpool Street station.</li>
	<li>Start at London Wall, All Hallows Church (stop U), approximately 275m from Liverpool Street station, and serve Old Broad Street, near Great Winchester Street (stop R) as normal</li>
</ul>

<p>They will return to normal when the bus station reopens.</p>

<p>Route 153</p>

<p>Route&nbsp;153 will continue to start and finish at Moorgate, Finsbury Square (stop J), approximately 500m from Liverpool Street station. It was temporarily re-routed to Moorgate, Finsbury Square to maintain&nbsp; reliability during roadworks and road closures. The route will be restored to the bus station when it reopens.</p>
</div>
 
