<h2>Sutton Hospital - Route S3</h2>


<p><strong>Bus route S3 diverted to Belmont station until further notice.</strong></p>
<p>From Saturday 28 October 2017 until further notice, route S3 no longer serves Sutton Hospital (bus stop K) or Cotswold Road (bus stops E and F).</p>
<p>Route S3 now runs the full length of Downs Road to Belmont rail station. The last stop is stop D and the first stop is stop C. It continues to serve stops M and N in Downs Road (near Cotswold Road) and stop L in the grounds of Royal Marsden Hospital.</p>
<p>This is due to the redevelopment of Sutton Hospital. We are no longer able to use the bus stop in the hospital grounds.</p>
<p>We are working with the developers to reinstate route S3 to the redeveloped site in the future.</p>
